  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a Magic action, you cause yourself to emit an aura of sunlight that lasts for 1 minute or until you dismiss it (no action required). You emit Bright Light in a 60-foot radius and Dim Light for an additional 30 feet. Your enemies in the Bright Light have Disadvantage on saving throws against your [[/item Radiance of the Dawn]] and any spell that deals Fire or Radiant damage.</p><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your Wisdom modifier (minimum of once), and you regain all expended uses when you finish a Long Rest.</p><section id=\"secret-iWkyJvoBe8LFDGvR\" class=\"secret\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>This feature includes a target template of 60 feet for tracking the emitted Bright Light and an Active Effect for marking affected creatures but it does not automate the Disadvantage.</p></section>",
